TITLE: Using Hypothetical useOnlineStatus Hook in React Components (Before Extraction)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how two React components, `StatusBar` and `SaveButton`, would consume a hypothetical `useOnlineStatus` hook to manage their online/offline state. This example highlights the duplicated logic that motivates creating a custom hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/reusing-logic-with-custom-hooks.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
function StatusBar() {
